title: Something Glowing
lyrics: Indefinite and definitely dreamed about there's something.

Some terrible kaleidoskull
That ever so gently destroys
The minds of those who believe it.
Now there's a lightbulb at the bottom of the sea. It's glowing.
It's like sunlight, the upside-downness of it... It's saying something.
I can tell it's there by the way it's not quite there.
